'''Samba Gadjigo''' (yavutse 12 Ukwakira 1954), ni umukinnyi wa filimi muri  [[Senegali|Senegal]]  kandi  akaba umwanditsi wa filimi. <ref name="mtholyoke">https://www.mtholyoke.edu/people/samba-gadjigo</ref> Azwi cyane nkumuyobozi wa firime ''Sembene izwi cyane!'' . <ref name="Sembene">https://www.mtholyoke.edu/media/gadjigos-film-voice-and-vision-africa</ref>

== Ubuzima bwite ==
Yavutse ku ya 12 Ukwakira 1954 i Kidira, muri [[Senegali]] . Yarangije muri kaminuza ya Dakar na Ecole Normale Supérieure de Dakar. Hanyuma yabonye impamyabumenyi ya PhD muri kaminuza ya Illinois muri Urbana-Champaign . Kugeza ubu akora nka Porofeseri w’igifaransa muri Mount Holyoke College, Massachusetts kuva 1986. <ref>https://arts.stanford.edu/event/66183/</ref>

== Umwuga ==
Muri 2015, yayoboye filime ''Sembene!'' hamwe na Jason Silverman. <ref>https://radioplasma.com/2019/05/04/samba-gadjigo-we-are-made-of-stories/</ref> Iyi filime yari ishingiye ku buzima bw'umukinnyi wa filime wo muri Senegal Ousmane Sembène bakunze kwita se wa sinema nyafurika . Filime yerekanwe bwa mbere kumugaragaro muri Sundance Film Festival muri Utah.  Filime yakiriwe neza <ref>https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/sembene_2015/</ref> <ref>[https://www.vulture.com/2015/12/bilge-ebiris-top-10-movies-of-2015.html/ https://www.vulture.com/2015/12/bilge-ebiris-top-10-movies-of-2015.html]</ref> kandi yegukana ibihembo byinshi ndetse no gushimirwa mubirori mpuzamahanga bya firime. <ref>[https://www.mtholyoke.edu/media/professors-film-recognized-internationally https://www.mtholyoke.edu/media/professors-film-recognized-internationall]</ref> Iyi filime yabaye uwanyuma kuri Kamera d'Or mu iserukiramuco rya sinema rya Cannes <ref>https://www.mtholyoke.edu/media/professors-film-screen-cannes-festival</ref> ndetse yegukana igihembo cya Jury mu iserukiramuco rya Filime rya Luxor African 2016. Yatsindiye kandi Prix de la Jeuness muri Escales Documentaires de Libreville 2017 hanyuma yegukana igihembo cya Paul Robeson mu iserukiramuco rya Filime ryabirabura rya Newark 2016. Filime yaje kubona igihembo cyinyandiko nziza muri Emerge Film Festival. <ref name="mtholyoke">{{Template:Cite web}}<cite class="citation web cs1" data-ve-ignore="true">[https://www.mtholyoke.edu/people/samba-gadjigo "Samba Gadjigo: Helen Day Gould Professor of French"]. mtholyoke<span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved <span class="nowrap">30 October</span> 2020</span>.</cite></ref>

Muri 2016, Gadjigo yahawe igihembo cy'ishami rya Bourse. Usibye gukora firime, ni n'umwanditsi wamamaye kandi yagize uruhare ''muri Sinema nyafurika nuburenganzira bwa muntu'', ''ubushakashatsi mubuvanganzo nyafurika'', ''nintererano mubushakashatsi bwabirabura'' . <ref name="mtholyoke">{{Template:Cite web}}<cite class="citation web cs1" data-ve-ignore="true">[https://www.mtholyoke.edu/people/samba-gadjigo "Samba Gadjigo: Helen Day Gould Professor of French"]. mtholyoke<span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved <span class="nowrap">30 October</span> 2020</span>.</cite></ref> Muri Werurwe 2016, yahawe igihembo cya Meribeth E. Cameron Igihembo cya Bourse yo muri Mount Holyoke College. <ref>https://www.mtholyoke.edu/media/four-mhc-professors-receive-faculty-awards</ref>

